These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lemon, nectarine, onion, pear
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, chess, video-games, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, biathlon, lacrosse, sailing
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
 2. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
 4. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person eating pear##6
 5. the person eating onion is somewhere to the right of the person eating lemon##5
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 7. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not to the left of the person eating nectarine##8
 8. the person eating nectarine is not the person who's sport is sailing##6
 9. the person eating lemon is not the person who's hobby is gardening##6
10. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
11. the person eating nectarine is not to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8
12. the person eating nectarine is in an even position##4
13. the person eating pear is not to the right of the person who's sport is sailing##8
14. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person who's sport is lacrosse##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Food    | lemon         | pear     | onion     | nectarine         |
| Hobby   | chess | gardening    | video-games     | board-games |
| Sport   | cricket       | biathlon | sailing | lacrosse       |

