.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda, 7up, cola
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, manager, police-officer, project-manager
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, basketball, climbing, sailing
 1. the police-officer is not to the right of the project-manager##8
 2. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the person drinking cola is the manager##1
 5. the writer is not the person drinking 7up##6
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the right of the writer##1
 8. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
 9. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
10. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage   | 7up          | tea      | cola      | mirinda   |
| Job        | police-officer     | writer | manager | project-manager      |
| Sport      | sailing | basketball    | biathlon  | climbing |

