.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, rock-climbing, camping, magic-tricks
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, gospel, salsa, dubstep
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, snowmobile, subway
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
 2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
 3. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
 4. the fan of gospel is somewhere to the left of the person driving the subway##5
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is not the fan of soul##6
 6. the fan of soul is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 7. the fan of soul is not to the right of the fan of dubstep##8
 8. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an even position##4
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | camping  | rock-climbing | magic-tricks | video-games |
| Music-Genre   | gospel  | soul      | dubstep | salsa        |
| Transport     | quad-bike | snowmobile       | subway    | motorbike     |

