.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-4::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: musical, drama, romance, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, r&b, disco, country
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, egyptian, french, dutch
 1. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the fan of country##1
 2. the egyptian is not to the left of the fan of r&b##8
 3. the fan of country is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
 4. the person watching musical movies is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is not to the right of the egyptian##8
 6. the french is not to the right of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 7. the fan of disco is somewhere to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##5
 8. the dutch is somewhere to the right of the egyptian##5
 9. the russian is on the left of the french##1
10. the person watching fantasy movies is the french##1
11. the fan of classical is somewhere to the right of the fan of r&b##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical   | fantasy | drama    | romance |
| Music-Genre   | disco    | r&b     | classical   | country     |
| Nationality   | russian | french   | egyptian | dutch    |

