.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, dancing, rock-climbing, writing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, romance, time-travel, documentary
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: weightlifting, ice-hockey, water-polo, badminton
 1. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
 2. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1
 3. the person watching horror movies is on the far right##1
 4. the person who's hobby is writing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1
 6. the person watching documentary movies is not the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##6
 7. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6
 8. the person watching romance movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is not to the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##8
10. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
11. the person who's sport is badminton is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing       | board-games | dancing  | writing    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel       | documentary    | romance | horror    |
| Sport         | badminton | weightlifting   | water-polo   | ice-hockey |

