.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-6::.
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, cucumber, cherry, broccoli
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, sports, comedy, scientific
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, malaysian, nigerian, turkish
 1. the person eating cherry is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
 2. the person watching scientific movies is not the malaysian##6
 3. the nigerian is somewhere between the person eating cucumber and the person watching scientific movies##7
 4. the malaysian is not to the left of the person watching sports movies##8
 5. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
 6. the nigerian is the person watching thriller movies##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the right of the person watching comedy movies##5
 8. the turkish is between the person eating raspberry and the nigerian##2
 9. the person watching scientific movies is not to the right of the person eating raspberry##8
10. the person eating cherry is not to the right of the person eating broccoli##8
11. the australian is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |   3    |     4     |
| Food          | cucumber      | cherry      | broccoli | raspberry |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | thriller    | scientific | sports     |
| Nationality   | australian    | nigerian | turkish  | malaysian |

