1. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
2. the person eating watermelon is somewhere between the person eating pomegranate and the person eating artichoke##7
3. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan of electronic##3
4. the fan of electronic is not to the right of the person drinking sprite##8
5. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere to the right of the person drinking milk##5
6. the person eating watermelon is not to the right of the person drinking water##8
7. the person eating pomegranate is the fan of folk##1
8. the person eating pomegranate is somewhere between the fan of d&b and the person drinking milk##7
9. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

