There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, russian, chinese, argentine
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, taxi, trike, tram
 1. the person who's hobby is video-games is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8
 2. the argentine is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the chinese##7
 3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
 4. the person driving the taxi is on the far left##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the canadian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
 7. the argentine is on the left or right of the canadian##3
 8. the canadian is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##5
 9. the person who's hobby is sudoku is not to the left of the person driving the airplane##8
10. the person driving the trike is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8
11. the canadian is not to the left of the person who's hobby is reading##8
12. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
13. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
14. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |      3      |     4      |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing    | video-games | reading | sudoku    |
| Nationality   | chinese  | argentine    | canadian      | russian |
| Transport     | taxi | airplane          | tram      | trike       |

