 4. the journalist is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left or right of the dressmaker##3
 6. the person watching mystery movies is the journalist##1
 7. the firefighter is not to the right of the journalist##8
 8. the journalist is not to the left of the person drinking coffee##8
 9. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the person watching western movies##5
10. the journalist is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
11. the dressmaker is not the person drinking fanta##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3     |      4      |
