.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-8-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, mexican, american, pakistani
4 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, hamster, turtle
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, water-polo, rowing, surfing
1. the owner of the goat is the person who's sport is cricket##1
2. the mexican is not to the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
3. the person who's sport is surfing is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the turtle##2
4. the japanese is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the mexican is not the person who's sport is rowing##6
6. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the pakistani##1
